ctives from dozens of experts speaking in many different languages on what it’s like to open up heritage content online. \n\nWe asked all our guests the same questions:\n1️⃣  What are the main benefits of open GLAM?\n2️⃣  What are the barriers?\n3️⃣. Could you share something someone else told you that opened up your eyes and mind about open GLAM?\n4️⃣. Do you have a personal message to those hesitating to open up collections?\n\nWe hope that you enjoy, and learn more, by listening to the distinct voices helping make GLAM collections as openly accessible, shareable, and reusable as possible – the greatest manifestation of their public value. Going open is the best way to celebrate GLAMs’ mission in the digital era.\n\n——————\n \n👉  Learn more about CC's Open Culture VOICES Series: https://creativecommons.org/about/program-areas/arts-culture/voices-vlog/\n👉  Learn more about CC’s Open Culture Program:  https://creativecommons.org/about/program-areas/arts-culture/", "channel_id": "UCTwECeGqMZee77BjdoYtI2Q", "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTwECeGqMZee77BjdoYtI2Q", "duration": 133, "view_count": 3842, "age_limit": 0, "webpage_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w2S5Ov-7Mzo", "categories": ["Nonprofits & Activism"], "tags": [], "playable_in_embed": true, "live_status": "not_live", "media_type": "video", "_format_sort_fields": ["quality", "res", "fps", "hdr:12", "source", "vcodec", "channels", "acodec", "lang", "proto"], "automatic_captions": {}, "subtitles": {"en": [{"ext": "json3", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/api/timedtext?v=w2S5Ov-7Mzo&ei=puFRauDJPLzFy_sP_N6w0AQ&caps=asr&opi=112496729&xoaf=5&xowf=1&hl=en&ip=0.0.0.0&ipbits=0&expire=1783776279&sparams=ip%2Cipbits%2Cexpire%2Cv%2Cei%2Ccaps%2Copi%2Cxoaf&signature=48F4979E2B11BFBC8E123FA16552A7557E1C2E9C.47D6921FF9855695F9DB3F91C289B07512904466&key=yt8&lang=en&fmt=json3", "name": "English", "impersonate": true}, {"ext": "srv1", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/api/timedtext?v=w2S5Ov-7Mzo&ei=puFRauDJPL